examples.en: She cavorted about in the water.
The kids were allowed to cavort in the water.
The photograph shows him cavorting with two young women.
examples.ru: На этой фотографии он забавляется с двумя молодыми женщинами.

examples.en: She was cavorting topless with her lover by the side of a pool.
